00:00:05.288 --> 00:00:08.954
Seeker: What do you think of homosexuality?

00:00:09.735 --> 00:00:13.122
Shri Mataji: Will you beat me if I say something?

00:00:13.242 --> 00:00:16.755
First guarantee that, then I’ll tell you.

00:00:18.952 --> 00:00:24.016
It is not natural, my child. Homosexuality is not natural.

00:00:24.136 --> 00:00:29.582
But unnatural things we do in a natural
way many a times. The reason is this:

00:00:29.702 --> 00:00:35.307
Homosexuality, when I came ten years
back, was not known to people much.

00:00:35.427 --> 00:00:37.763
A little bit here and there.

00:00:37.883 --> 00:00:43.099
The reason it became very dominant
is because firstly, I personally think,

00:00:43.219 --> 00:00:47.365
the women were dominating,
they were trying to out beat them.

00:00:47.485 --> 00:00:52.678
Moreover to marry an American
woman means you are in for bankruptcy.

00:01:04.912 --> 00:01:12.475
I met a lady in New York, a very
rich lady, who came in a big Cadillac

00:01:12.595 --> 00:01:15.631
and she said, “You’ll meet my husband in San Diego.”

00:01:15.751 --> 00:01:18.099
The poor fellow was tattered and torn.

00:01:18.219 --> 00:01:25.847
She had got all this from her first husband, then
taken from second husband, then from third husband.

00:01:25.967 --> 00:01:33.270
These three husbands met me and they
were all in a mess and they had no money.

00:01:33.396 --> 00:01:40.037
They had this law if you marry a woman, it’s
terrible, you have to share everything that you have.

00:01:40.162 --> 00:01:43.900
In Australia, not share, you have to
give away everything that you have.

00:01:44.020 --> 00:01:48.368
This kind of a partiality started.
That’s one of the reasons.

00:01:48.428 --> 00:01:56.199
Secondly they became very dominating.
They’ve lost their feminine powers.

00:01:56.319 --> 00:02:02.195
A woman who has feminine power never
dominates you because she dominates in any case.

00:02:03.443 --> 00:02:09.966
She’s like the Mother Earth. She
knows how to absorb the problems,

00:02:10.086 --> 00:02:12.195
she knows how to solve the problems.

00:02:12.315 --> 00:02:19.784
Supposing my husband has any problem. He first
comes home, he shouts at me, screams at me, finished now.

00:02:19.904 --> 00:02:23.715
And then he tells me, “Now, what to do?”

00:02:25.410 --> 00:02:29.019
And I just smile because I know he doesn’t mean any
harm to me.

00:02:29.139 --> 00:02:33.860
It’s just the way he has to take it out on me.

00:02:33.980 --> 00:02:37.662
They’ve lost their power of femininity.

00:02:38.024 --> 00:02:44.649
So the men thought it’s better to have
man’s power, not to have a woman’s power.

00:02:44.769 --> 00:02:48.187
Because we have seen the women
like Mrs. Kennedy, now, look at her.

00:02:48.307 --> 00:02:50.840
Is she a woman or a man? I don’t know what to call her.

00:02:50.961 --> 00:02:57.627
She made such a thing out of her
life, something surprising and shocking.

00:02:57.747 --> 00:03:01.315
For us Indian women we can’t understand
because she was selling her underclothes

00:03:01.435 --> 00:03:05.076
and people from Australia ran all
the way to buy her underclothes.

00:03:05.196 --> 00:03:08.795
We couldn’t understand what is
happening to the men and to the women,

00:03:08.915 --> 00:03:12.715
the men becoming women and women
becoming men. It was a horrid stuff.

00:03:12.835 --> 00:03:19.555
As it is it was homosexuality because
they were not of different sexes left.

00:03:19.675 --> 00:03:24.644
So men took to homosexuality as a matter of convenience.

00:03:25.192 --> 00:03:32.361
Thirdly when a man gets possessed by a
woman he starts behaving like a woman.

00:03:32.481 --> 00:03:35.177
In America we had a boy like that.

00:03:35.303 --> 00:03:39.248
He used to behave like a woman, dress
up like a woman, walk about like a woman

00:03:39.368 --> 00:03:44.327
and he was a homosexual in the sense
that outwardly he was living like a man,

00:03:44.447 --> 00:03:49.832
looking like a man, but he was a woman inside.
When we removed his possession he became normal.

00:03:49.952 --> 00:03:54.515
We have so many homosexuals who came to
us. When they got realization now act normal.

00:03:54.635 --> 00:03:59.141
They are married and have children and
also women become women after realization.

00:03:59.261 --> 00:04:02.802
They become beautiful wives and very
sweet things

00:04:02.922 --> 00:04:05.855
and you like to marry them also.
